       para9a: "You are fully responsible and liable for the use of the Platform through your Account.",
       para9b: "You are solely responsible for the technical operation and maintenance of your internet connection, internal network, and all other systems that are relevant or necessary for undisturbed use of the Platform.",
       para9c: "Unless there is wilful misconduct or gross negligence on the part of OpinionBar, OpinionBar is not liable in any way for your (direct or indirect) damages or costs of whatsoever nature in connection with use of the Platform, the Account or the information shared on the Platform, such as, but not limited to, damages and costs due to the lack of a proper functioning of the Platform, technical faults, and unlawful information on the Platform. OpinionBar cannot be and is not responsible for compliance with your obligations rising from these Terms.",
       para9d: "A claim will in any case lapse if OpinionBar is not notified in writing of the claim within one (1) year of the discovery of an event or circumstance that gives rise to or could give rise to liability.",
       para9e: "Nothing in these Terms shall exclude or limit OpinionBar’s liability when it cannot be excluded or limited under applicable law. If, for whatever reason, OpinionBar is liable for any damage to you in connection with the Services, OpinionBar’s liability will be limited to an amount of EUR 100 or to the amount the insurance company of OpinionBar disburses in that specific case, whichever is lower.",
