       para10a: "You shall indemnify, defend, and hold harmless OpinionBar from any third-party claims, liability, damages and/or costs (including, but not limited to, attorney fees) arising from your use of the Platform, or violation of these Terms.",
       para10b: "OpinionBar preserves the right to assume the exclusive defence and control of any matter subject to indemnification by you, in which event you will assist and cooperate with OpinionBar asserting any available defences.",
