       hd3_ptAa: 'We collect Identity Data, Biographical Data, or Contact Data from you when you register to use the Platform ',
       registrationData: 'Registration Data',
       serviceandcommunicate: 'This personal data is used primarily to create and maintain your account on our Service and communicate with you regarding that account and for important information regarding our Service. Where allowed by law and when we obtained your consent for this, Registration Data may be used in connection with marketing communications.',
       whenProfile: 'When you create a Profile',
       profilewithpersonaldata: 'If you wish to participate in Surveys through our Platform, we will require that you complete a profile with personal data that is used match you with Surveys based on your background, demographics, etc.',
       profileData: 'Profile Data',
       biographicalData_userContent: 'Profile Data may include Contact Data, Biographical Data, User Content, Identity Data, or other categories of personal data requested on the profile page or related forms. You may generally choose what Profile Data to provide. In some cases, when you are selected for a Survey, we may ask for additional Profile Data if the Client requires additional specific information to determine a user’s suitability or for the Survey or further refine the User’s profile as appropriate in connection with the Survey. At the Client’s direction and subject to your rights under applicable law, we may also augment your Profile Data with additional information obtained from third party commercial sources.',
