       note: 'Note:',
       users_personalData: 'Users may choose not to include certain categories of Personal Data as part of their profile. If you do not wish for use to collect any category of personal data, do not provide it as part of your profile. You may not receive as many offers to participate in Surveys if your profile does not include information sufficient to place you in Surveys with specific criteria.',
