       business_CommercialPurposes: 'Business and Commercial Purposes of Processing',
       commercial_purposes: 'We use your information for the following business and commercial purposes:',
       heading4: 'How we use the Information we Collect',
       hd4_pt2: 'We use your information in the following ways:',
       providing_Services: 'Providing the Services',
       providing_Services1: 'We may use personal data we collect as we believe necessary or appropriate to operate, maintain, administer and improve the Services and conduct the Surveys, analyze and report results, and other appropriate processing. We may also use data you provide us to respond to your inquiries and otherwise deliver customer service or and to process any payments to you.',
       note4: 'Note',
       note5: 'Any Registration Data, Profile Data and Survey Data you choose to provide will be used as necessary to provide the Services and may be analyzed or transferred subject to your contract with us, and our contract with our Clients. You may choose to change any Registration or Profile Data that is part of your user account, however, once you have completed a Survey, the terms of your contract may result in the sale of that data and affect your rights in that data.',
       creatingAggregateData: 'Creating Aggregate Data',
       creatingAggregateData1: 'We will use Survey Data and Profile Data to create reports comprised of Aggregated Data that we will provide to our Clients, and we may otherwise use responses in accordance with standard market research industry practices and guidelines. We may also process information from Cookies and Similar Technologies, and other personal data collected through our Sites to analyze how our Services are used or perform, and other related matters.',
       communicatingwithYou: 'Communicating with You',
       communicatingwithYou1: 'We may also use your contact data to communicate with you regarding your account, for example, by sending you Service announcements, technical notices, updates, security alerts, and support and administrative messages. Consistent with our legitimate interests in direct marketing to our users, we may also use personal data we collect to communicate directly with you, including by sending you newsletters, promotions or information about new products and services. Your opt-out options for promotional communications are described below.',
       personalizingtheServices: 'Profiling/Personalization',
       personalizingtheServices1: 'We may use personal data we collect to personalize the Services, including to greet you by name, provide better Survey recommendations to you, tailor communications to your interests, and use the information to guide overall improvements to our products and the Services. We may also create and augment user profiles with include information such as Inference Data or certain Aggregate Data in order to better tailor the Surveys, assess Survey eligibility, and to augment your Survey responses.',
       improvingtheServices: 'Improving the Services',
       improvingtheServices1: 'We may use personal data we collect as we believe necessary or appropriate to analyze trends, administer or optimize the Services, monitor usage or traffic patterns (including to track users’ use of the Services) and gather certain Inference Data about our user base as a whole.',
       advertising: 'Advertising',
       advertising1: 'We do not sell or use personal data collected during Surveys for direct marketing or other advertising purposes. However, we may use personal data we collect from our Sites to deliver you advertising, including by serving and managing ads on the Services or on third party sites and to tailor ads based on your interests and browsing history. Please see below for additional information on how to manage the ads you see.',
