       //Information: 'With whom do you Share my Information?',
       Information1: 'Personal data we collect may be disclosed to a variety of parties, depending upon the purpose for which the information was provided and the context in which it was provided. The following describes how we may share the personal data we receive through our Services.',
       clients: 'Clients',
       clients1: 'Pursuant to our contract with the Client, and your contract with us to provide the Survey Data for compensation, we may share Survey Data and related Profile Data with the Client who requested that we host the Survey. In some circumstances, we may share personal data with commercial data suppliers so that we can obtain additional information relevant to a Survey, to better validate your Survey responses, so that we may share additional Aggregated Data with our Clients, or for other business purposes. Any Registration Data, and Survey Data may be shared with Clients for the purpose of Survey validation, except that this data will be identified by a randomly-generated ID number, and we will not share your name or other Registration Data with Clients. If you are a registered user who has consented to the installation of our web-browsing based Survey Cookie, we may share a randomly generated user ID and the information contained in or collected from the use of the tracking cookie with our Client.',
